results.title: Fine Art Print "Light at the End of the Tunnel" 8x12 B/w or Color
results.description:

The color 8x12 fine art photograph by Sweet T Photography is printed on Kodak Professional Endura Metallic Paper which gives it a beautiful depth and an almost three dimensional quality that just can't be achieved with ordinary photo papers. The gold and silver tones in this photo are spectacular when printed on this high quality metallic photo paper. 

The black and white image is printed on Kodak Professional Endura Lustre Paper. What we used to call matte, they now call lustre. I guess it is more glamorous that way ;)

results.title: Fine Art Canvas Print "If Heaven Has a Driveway" 32x48 Extra Large Wall Art
results.description:
Sweet Southern charm at its best. I imagine someone named Miss Lulabelle greeting you on the front porch with a glass of sweet tea and a smile. And as you're leaving, she's calling, "Y'all come back!" 
This is the most beautiful drive I have ever seen. This is the entrance to Wormsloe Plantation in Savannah, Georgia. These old oaks must have seen so much, the stories they could tell... Honestly and truly, I believe that if Heaven has a driveway, it will look just like this.  This driveway was featured in the movie, The Last Song. 

This 32x48 fine art photograph by Sweet T Photography is printed on fine artist canvas, stretched on a solid faced frame and completely finished all around with no staples and a sturdy black backer board.
